Day 5: Listen More, Speak Less!
👂 "Great Scrum Masters listen twice as much as they talk."  
👉 Tip: Let your team’s voice be heard. The more you listen, the more you understand and support their needs.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
